# Entertainment & Streaming Website Rules for AI Code Builders

## ⚠️ MANDATORY PRE-IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLIST ⚠️

1. 🎬 STREAMING REQUIREMENTS VALIDATION
   - [ ] Define content types
   - [ ] Plan streaming quality tiers
   - [ ] Identify user roles
   - [ ] List playback features
   - [ ] Document DRM requirements

2. 📱 RESPONSIVE DESIGN REQUIREMENTS
   - [ ] Desktop (1920px, 1440px, 1280px)
   - [ ] Tablet (1024px, 768px)
   - [ ] Mobile (428px, 375px, 320px)
   - [ ] Smart TV support

3. 🎯 CORE FEATURES CHECKLIST
   - [ ] Content catalog
   - [ ] Video player
   - [ ] User profiles
   - [ ] Recommendations
   - [ ] Search functionality
   - [ ] Watchlist
   - [ ] Continue watching
   - [ ] Subscription management

## 🏗️ Architecture Guidelines

### Component Structure
```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── layout/
│   │   ├── Header.tsx
│   │   ├── Footer.tsx
│   │   └── Navigation.tsx
│   ├── player/
│   │   ├── VideoPlayer.tsx
│   │   ├── Controls.tsx
│   │   ├── Quality.tsx
│   │   └── Subtitles.tsx
│   ├── catalog/
│   │   ├── ContentCard.tsx
│   │   ├── ContentGrid.tsx
│   │   ├── Categories.tsx
│   │   └── Filters.tsx
│   ├── user/
│   │   ├── Profile.tsx
│   │   ├── Watchlist.tsx
│   │   └── History.tsx
│   ├── subscription/
│   │   ├── Plans.tsx
│   │   ├── Payment.tsx
│   │   └── Benefits.tsx
│   └── common/
│       ├── SearchBar.tsx
│       ├── Recommendations.tsx
│       └── Notifications.tsx
├── pages/
│   ├── browse/
│   ├── watch/
│   ├── profile/
│   └── account/
└── styles/
    └── theme/
```

### Streaming Requirements
1. **Video Quality**
   - 4K (2160p)
   - Full HD (1080p)
   - HD (720p)
   - SD (480p)
   - Adaptive bitrate

2. **Audio Quality**
   - Dolby Digital
   - Stereo
   - Multiple languages
   - Audio description

3. **Playback Features**
   - Autoplay
   - Skip intro
   - Next episode
   - Playback speed
   - Quality selection

## 📊 Performance Requirements

1. **Streaming Performance**
   - Buffer management
   - Quality adaptation
   - Network optimization
   - CDN integration

2. **Content Loading**
   - Thumbnail optimization
   - Lazy loading
   - Preloading
   - Caching strategy

3. **Application Performance**
   - Quick start
   - Smooth navigation
   - Background loading
   - Memory management

## 🎥 Player Requirements

1. **Core Features**
   - Custom controls
   - Progress bar
   - Quality selector
   - Subtitle support
   - Picture-in-picture

2. **Advanced Features**
   - DRM support
   - Analytics tracking
   - Error recovery
   - Offline playback

## 📱 Device Support

1. **Multi-platform**
   - Web browsers
   - Mobile devices
   - Smart TVs
   - Gaming consoles

2. **Device Features**
   - Device detection
   - Capability check
   - Adaptive UI
   - Platform APIs

## 🔄 Implementation Process

1. **Setup Phase**
   - [ ] CDN setup
   - [ ] DRM integration
   - [ ] Player development
   - [ ] Analytics setup

2. **Core Features**
   - [ ] Content catalog
   - [ ] Video playback
   - [ ] User profiles
   - [ ] Search system

3. **Enhanced Features**
   - [ ] Recommendations
   - [ ] Watchlist
   - [ ] Continue watching
   - [ ] Social features

4. **Platform Support**
   - [ ] Mobile apps
   - [ ] TV apps
   - [ ] Console apps
   - [ ] Cross-platform sync

## 📈 Analytics Integration

1. **Playback Analytics**
   - Watch time
   - Quality metrics
   - Buffer events
   - Error tracking

2. **User Analytics**
   - Viewing habits
   - Content preferences
   - Device usage
   - Subscription data

## 🔍 Quality Assurance

1. **Streaming Quality**
   - Playback testing
   - Network conditions
   - Device compatibility
   - DRM validation

2. **Application Quality**
   - Performance testing
   - Cross-platform testing
   - Security testing
   - Load testing

## 📝 Documentation Requirements

1. **Technical Documentation**
   - Player integration
   - DRM setup
   - API documentation
   - Deployment guide

2. **User Documentation**
   - Help center
   - FAQs
   - Troubleshooting
   - Device support

## 🔐 Security Requirements

1. **Content Security**
   - DRM implementation
   - Copy protection
   - Geo-restriction
   - Access control

2. **User Security**
   - Authentication
   - Payment security
   - Data protection
   - Session management

## 💰 Monetization Features

1. **Subscription Plans**
   - Tier management
   - Payment processing
   - Trial periods
   - Family sharing

2. **Revenue Optimization**
   - Upsell opportunities
   - Retention strategies
   - Churn prevention
   - Analytics tracking

## 🎯 Personalization

1. **User Preferences**
   - Viewing history
   - Content preferences
   - Language settings
   - Playback settings

2. **Recommendations**
   - Content discovery
   - Personalized lists
   - Similar content
   - Trending content 